titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on diamino imid sp.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 4/1/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1997, the duty on 1-H-Naphth (2.3-f1-)isoindole-1,3,5,10(2H)-tetrone,4,11-Diamino (diamino imid sp.)
